screen_name: @osutein Day 65 for me. When I rang for help at day 8, begging to be knocked out from rigors, fever, diarrhoea, gasping for breath, hr of 200...i was told there’s no help because I could talk on the phone. Since then, tremor, myalgia, SOB, chest pain, fatigue for two months. Mild!

@preshitorian Thank you for tweeting your journey. Day 63 for me, still have tremor, “fizzing” sensation in my limbs, SOB, chest pain, fatigue, three periods in six weeks, loss of appetite, stomach cramps, hot flushes and chills. It is nice to know im not alone.
